me.taylorkelly.mywarp.teleport

Class SafeTeleportManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.taylorkelly.mywarp.teleport.SafeTeleportManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TeleportManager

    public class SafeTeleportManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements TeleportManager
    A TeleportManager implementation that checks if a teleport destination is safe for a normal entity. If not, a safe position is searched within a defined margin. If one is found the entity is teleported there, if not, no teleport occurs.
